    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't merely a car; it is a silver-maned masterpiece waiting to be unleashed. Picture yourself behind the wheel as the moonlight dances across its flawless, liquid-metal curves, turning every street corner into a cinematic event. Inside, you are enveloped in the intoxicating aroma of hand-finished leather and the cool touch of polished chrome, a sanctuary of craftsmanship that feels as if it were tailored specifically for you. The engine doesn't just start; it awakens with a soulful hum that promises effortless power and a grace that commands respect. This is more than a drive\u2014it's a legacy of elegance and a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that possesses a spirit all its own.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
